title: J. Geils Band - The Best of the J. Geils Band - 2006 [flac]
description:
The Best of the J. Geils Band - Capitol, 2006 [flac]

This is the 2nd the album with the same title; the first one in 1979 only covered the early history of the band. This one includes the band's biggest hits from the 1980s.
